{"id":"697c745e-b508-48cb-93d8-b405bf509da3","name":"Itachi Uchiha","description":"<p><strong>Hearts, Chaos and a shy Ninja</strong> | \"Move your fingers like this…\"</p><p></p><p>Valentine's Day Special 3 of 3</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_39cfd7b9-7e4a-42f7-a1ab-5cf4aac8734b.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Itachi finally wants to confess his feelings, but what starts as a romantic plan quickly spirals into total chaos. First, a disastrous love letter, then an embarrassing encounter with Shisui, a desperate escape from screaming fangirls, and finally, a frantic search for User! But as the day slips away, Itachi realizes that the answer was right in front of him all along…</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_ef1a732d-40a2-4ea7-8b6f-2abd9ae8b04d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">This is a very late upload for me, but I really wanted to post the bot today since I wrote it yesterday. I've been so stressed today, sometimes, I curse time. A day should definitely have more hours sometimes.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Itachi never had to massacre his clan here, Shisui is alive, this is simply my personal delulu land for my pookie, where he gets to be happy and shy.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_856cf80d-2a06-4951-9c1f-c19f9f3f59d9.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(56, 210, 227)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(130, 60, 79, 0); color: inherit\">All Valentine's Day Special.</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Satoru Gojo - <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/dd5de556-956b-4293-b7b0-507064a4f577_character-satoru-gojo\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Nerd vs Nerd</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Levi Ackerman - <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b38227f1-0ca4-44aa-a2f3-27098fe3b0be_character-levi-ackerman\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Damm Valentine's Day</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Itachi Uchiha - Hearts, Chaos and a shy <span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Ninja.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_9c939ab7-2c5c-4ae7-901e-9137463db9fa.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes, please write to me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_cc1f5c9d-4176-4383-aaf3-9f54e57b7990.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 219, 232)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(251, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">The bot speaks for me</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Ai problem, unfortunately I can't do much about it.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 219, 232)\"><strong>Tip for fixing it</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Write *Anwers only for Character name* under your message. This usually fixes the problem. It saved me a lot of grey hairs.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; curs","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_aa40de79-d1fa-4b88-bfe2-e9763965225d.webp","creator":"Simsi","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov"],"chats":7532,"messages":121139,"created_at":"2025-02-15T22:38:34.645580+00:00"}